Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I noticed something — my automated agents were still telling last week's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}9 years in crypto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}AI trades my thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I looked at the four agents running in the background — the tweet-writer, the long-form poster, the interview bot, the comment collector.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}All of them were speaking in the voice I'd written a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That voice was built on top of the strategy I'd already killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meaning — my mouth had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}My stand-ins were still reading from the old script.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.46,0:00:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}When the story changes direction, every automation still speaking the old direction has to change with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Including the automated versions of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Otherwise you'll contradict yourself in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That day I wiped all four agents and rewrote them from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Every new prompt starts from one phrase: if I can, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 13 tomorrow — the bot lied about closing my position.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.07,0:01:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow along.
